  <description type="morphology">Bracts 4–7, imbricate, circular to ovate, 1–1.5 mm. Flowers brown or maroon, 1.5–2 mm; sepals similar to bracts; stylar column with apex expanded to 1 mm diam., papillose along margins; anthers 15–21, in ring of ca. 3 rows; ovules mostly 120–200. Seeds mostly 120–200. 2n = 60 + 0–1B.</description>
